    <note>Li(2) Shiheng [1079] Cao(1) Liyong's [8133] and Cao(1) Cong's [7357] father-in-law. A brother or cousin, Shigun [3526], was Zhang(1) Hui(4)'s [7157] son-in-law. His wife, born Lei, who is identified with the choronym Fengyi was almost certainly a daughter of Lei(1) Dexiang [967]. Fan Zhongyan, WJ, 11.16a-21a; XCB, 44.14a-14b, 54.3a, 57.7a, 63.2a (n.), 63.1b-2a, 69.1a, 73.7a, 80.8b, 83.3a, 84.4a, 91.6b, 92.5a, 99.9a, 111.13a; Xia Song, WJ, 2.7b; SHY:SH, 49.10b-11a. CBD, 2, 939.</note>
